(8, 2, '', 1, 4, '订单状态', '<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">　　<strong>1、订单提交成功后还可以修改收货信息吗?</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">　　您好，订单在被商家接受之前您可以在订单页面取消订单并重新下单。为保证商品送达准确无误，订单在被接受后无法修改收货信息，请您谅解。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">　　<strong>2、怎么查看我的订单状态?</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">　　B2B2C电商平台商城将各种状态显示在订单详情页面，此种方式让您更好的了解订单情况，及时跟踪订单状态，以下是订单状态的简单说明： \r\n在等待收货过程中，可在网站“我的商城—我的订单”中查询订单状态，了解订单处理及商品配送进度。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">　　<strong>3、关于订单的取消，怎么操作?</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">　　如订单未被商家接受，您可在订单页取消订单并重新下单，如需取消订单商品，可通过B2B2C电商平台商城“我的商城—我的订单”中的订单修改功能进行修改。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">　　</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;"><b>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 订单状态查询详解：</b></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src="/data/upload/shop/editor/20150320113244_37424.jpg" alt="" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;"><b><br />\r\n</b></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;"><b><img src="/data/upload/shop/editor/20150320113254_28034.jpg" alt="" /><br />\r\n</b></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;"><b><br />\r\n</b></span> \r\n</p>', 1389864697),
(9, 2, '', 1, 1, '新用户注册', '<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">　　· 欢迎注册</span><strong><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">B2B2C电商平台商城</span></strong><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">!</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">　　· 请点击 【注册】，按照以下注册提示操作即可!</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">　　<strong>· 新用户注册步骤详解如下：</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">　　· 1.进入B2B2C电商平台商城首页，请点击左上角【注册】：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">　　<img src="/data/upload/shop/editor/20150320105319_96802.jpg" alt="" /></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">　　</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; · 2、按照网页提示，填写准确的注册信息后点击【立即注册】。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src="/data/upload/shop/editor/20150320105342_27306.jpg" alt="" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">　　· 3、系统会提示注册成功，请尽快完善个人信息资料并跳转到用户中心。暂时没完善个人资料，完全不影响购物体验。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">　　· 注册成功后，就可以开始您的购物之旅了!</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', 1389864697),
(10, 2, '', 1, 3, '购物指南', '<p>\r\n	<strong><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 购物流程</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;"><br />\r\n</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;"><img src="/data/upload/shop/editor/20141226161001_49894.jpg" alt="" /><br />\r\n</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;"><br />\r\n</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 用户购物步骤详解如下：</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 注册登录网站后，通过搜索或者直接找到想要买的宝贝，仔细浏览商品详细描述，确认购买时，请点击立即购买或者加入购物车结算：</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;"><br />\r\n</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1、找到要购买的宝贝，加入购物车或者点击立即购买</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;"><img src="/data/upload/shop/editor/20150320112148_64236.jpg" alt="" /><br />\r\n</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;"><br />\r\n</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2、进入购物车结算付款</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;"><img src="/data/upload/shop/editor/20150320112852_33623.jpg" alt="" /><br />\r\n</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;"><br />\r\n</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;"><br />\r\n</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 3、在购物车找到您刚才准备购买的订单商品，填写核对购物信息</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;"><img src="/data/upload/shop/editor/20150320112910_29945.jpg" alt="" /><br />\r\n</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;"><br />\r\n</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 4、仔细核对收货人信息、支付方式、是否需要开具发票、购买留言及是否使用账户预存款结算等信息，核对无误后（若有误可以随时点击修改），提交订单，进入支付页面</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;"><img src="/data/upload/shop/editor/20150320112947_83298.jpg" alt="" /><br />\r\n</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;"><br />\r\n</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 5、选择支付宝支付（如果您还没有开通支付宝账户，请参照如何注册支付宝，先在支付宝平台申请一个支付宝账户），确认提交支付</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;"><img src="/data/upload/shop/editor/20150320113004_58548.jpg" alt="" /><br />\r\n</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;"><br />\r\n</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 6、按照支付宝提示，用自己的支付宝账户完成订单付款，正式完成订单提交。</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;"><img src="/data/upload/shop/editor/20150320113022_71880.jpg" alt="" /><br />\r\n</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;"><br />\r\n</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp;在线完成付款后，订单正式生效，等待卖家发货。用户随时可在用户中心查看订单状态或者注意收阅平台</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">订单状态提醒</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">的短信和邮件。</span></strong> \r\n</p>', 1389864697),
